71.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/alfredo-sauce-730x1042.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/alfredo-sauce-700x999.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/alfredo-sauce-550x785.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/alfredo-sauce-156x223.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/alfredo-sauce.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-ingredients\"\u003eIngredients\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eButter\u003c/strong\u003e – Unsalted butter.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHeavy Cream\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGarlic\u003c/strong\u003e – Fresh minced garlic.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eItalian Seasoning\u003c/strong\u003e – Use store-bought or \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/italian-seasoning/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003emake your own\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eParmesan Cheese\u003c/strong\u003e – Grated Parmesan cheese.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSalt \u0026amp; Black Pepper\u003c/strong\u003e – To taste.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eWhile some like to thicken sauce with cornstarch, I will sometimes add a tablespoon or two of plain Greek yogurt to this recipe. But it’s not necessary, just an option. \u003cbr/\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" data-pin-title=\"easy Alfredo sauce\" width=\"1500\" height=\"2250\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-156x234.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-640x960.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201500%202250\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe.jpg 1333w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-200x300.jpg 200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-683x1024.jpg 683w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-1365x2048.jpg 1365w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-67x100.jpg 67w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-40x60.jpg 40w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-750x1125.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-730x1095.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-700x1050.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-550x825.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-156x234.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe-640x960.jpg 640w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/easy-alfredo-sauce-recipe.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-directions\"\u003eDirections\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn a saucepan, melt butter and lightly sauté the minced garlic in the butter for 1-2 minutes.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eNext, stir in the heavy whipping cream and Italian seasoning. Whisk so everything gets warm and well combined. Simmer on medium heat. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThen stir in the Parmesan cheese. Continue to stir until the cheese melts and the mixture becomes a sauce. Taste and season with salt and pepper to your liking. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-storage-and-reheating-tips\"\u003eStorage and  Reheating Tips \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis sauce is best when made and served immediately. If you have leftovers, store them in an airtight container in the refrigerator. To reheat, add a splash of cream or milk to the leftovers and heat them on the stovetop at low heat. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" data-pin-title=\"easy Alfredo sauce\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/